content: Stickers can't be used for WhatsApp. Unlike other Disney Apps, there's no refund buttons in Google Play. I wrote to Disney Support requesting for a refund. They took 1 week to come back with a solution that was not applicable [They thought I purchased the App via an IOS device when I purchase it on an Android device]. Till date, I'm still waiting for my refund.
